Title: The Mighty Ducks/D2: The Mighty Ducks 2-Pack

reviewText: if you enjoy stories about an underdog or enjoy watching hockey then these two movies are for you. if you are a fan of emilio estevez then you need to own these movies. emilio shows that he can hold his own despite the fact of who his father is. its fun to see how the charaters have grown and changed between the time of the two movies. its fun to see how the original cast interacts with the new charaters in the second movie. the new characters add a different type of slapstick comedy. these movies are a great family movies to watch on a friday or saturday night. if you own or collect disney movies then you need the spend the money to own these movies.
